{
  "stem": "1581.2",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "You got hit over the head with a new terrible event.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And it took you a while to overcome the shock.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "But then you adjusted to the new situation, although everyone became worse as the time went by.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So when we were in Eibenschutz, I had a job.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I was newly married.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We were very happy.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And life became halfway tolerable.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We were now in a little town.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The Czech population was completely on our side and helped us in every way they could.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So it was a bearable situation.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I didn't need special ration.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Because there was plenty of food.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "The Czechs supplied us with it.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We had-- of course we had to wear the yellow star.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But I was the only Jew who drove a car.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Because I had to go twice a week to Brno.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes, for me.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "There was no other car, no other Jew who could drive a car.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I was stopped all the time.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Because there were always road checks.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And they were very much surprised that I had a valid license to drive.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, not really.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Because at that time, I was awfully young.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And as I said, we always lived only for the future.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "As the years go-- went by, to the refugee camp, came a group of coal miners.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "There was a coal mine in-- near Ivancice.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And I was also in charge of the coal miners.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And when, in 1941, when the transports started, [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] I was told that I have nothing to fear, because my services are essential.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And I will not be transported out.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "But these transport became a real horror.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Nobody knew where they were going.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
